provider of water pipe rehabilitation services based in moncton, new brunswick,
canada.
(2)in
february2009, 3m (industrial and transportation business) purchased the
assets of compac corp.s pressure sensitive adhesive tape business, a global
leader in providing custom solutions in coating, laminating and converting
flexible substrates headquartered in hackettstown, n.j.
(3)in
