percent of the outstanding shares of meguiars international, uk, a distributor
of meguiars inc. products based in daventry, united kingdom.
(4)in
july2009, 3m (consumer and office business) purchased the ace branded
(and related brands) elastic bandage, supports and thermometer product lines,
which are sold broadly through consumer channels in north america.
purchased
