assets that will be amortized on a straight-line basis over a weighted-average
life of eight years (lives ranging from three to 12 years) and $8 million of
indefinite-lived intangible assets related to the well-recognized ace brand.
acquired identifiable intangible assets for which significant assumed renewals
or extensions of underlying arrangements impacted the determination of their
useful lives were not material.
